Assuming you have a Blitz screen (eg from FindScreen 0) and want to send it
to the back:

Set up a pointer to your screen:

FindScreen 0,"Workbench"
*scr.Screen=Peek.l(Addr Screen (0))

Put it to the back:

ScreenToBack_ *scr

Or to the front:

ScreenToFront_ *scr

This is all from memory, but I think it'll work.

