Newtype .MUI_Command
  *mc_Name.b
  *mc_Template.b
  mc_Parameters.l
  *mc_Hook.b
  mc_Reserved.l[5]
End Newtype

I'm using the following code to add an ARexx command:

Dim arexx.MUI_Command(1)
